snippet.title: Oh My Godheads | Release Trailer | Square Enix Collective | PEGI
snippet.description:
Frantic local multiplayer game Oh My Godheads is out now on PC, Xbox One and PS4! Grab a seat on the couch, a controller and play with family and friends! 

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/522740/Oh_My_Godheads/
Xbox One: https://www.microsoft.com/en-gb/store/p/oh-my-godheads/bz8jx8nk5x4n
PS4: https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/product/EP0082-CUSA09345_00-OMGHBASEGAME0001
